# Frontend Rules (master-foundry)

## Stack
- TypeScript strict mode, ES2020 target, ES module syntax
- Foundry VTT v12 module API
- Build: tsc (no bundler)

## Patterns
- Use Foundry VTT API patterns: Hooks, game global, Actor/Item documents
- Foundry ambient types declared in src/types/foundry-ambient.d.ts
- WebSocket communication with master-server backend
- UI templates use Handlebars (.hbs) in templates/
- Styles in styles/ directory

## Module Structure
- Entry point: src/main.ts
- Services: audio capture/playback, character generation
- Schema: blueprint/schema extraction from Foundry actors
- Skills: system skill adapters for different RPG systems
- Utils: field-tree builder, session manager, data sanitizer

## TypeScript Config
- strict: true, noImplicitAny: true, strictNullChecks: true, noImplicitReturns: true
- noUnusedLocals: false, noUnusedParameters: false
- Module resolution: node

## Build
- npm run build (tsc)
- npm run watch (tsc --watch)
